no problem at all.

44
00:02:10,780 --> 00:02:11,780
It would be my pleasure.

45
00:02:11,820 --> 00:02:15,240
Oh, that's really sweet of you
to offer, Rarity,

46
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:17,250
