do that.

47
00:02:17,250 --> 00:02:18,710
It would be so much work.

48
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:19,960
This dress is fine.

49
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,830
Twilight Sparkle,

50
00:02:21,880 --> 00:02:24,250
I insist on making you
a new dress.

51
