But --
Not another word.

52
00:02:25,710 --> 00:02:27,880
I won't take "no"
for an answer.

53
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:30,180
Well...in that case,

54
00:02:30,180 --> 00:02:32,510
thank you
for your generosity, Rarity.

55
00:02:32,550 --> 00:02:34,100
