74
00:03:15,010 --> 00:03:17,600
Didn't quite work.

75
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:18,930
Hmm.

76
00:03:20,020 --> 00:03:21,940
Idea!

77
00:03:21,980 --> 00:03:25,520
I'll make you an outfit
for the gala, too, Rainbow Dash!

78
00:03:27,570 --> 00:03:28,980
Outfit for the what now?

79
00:03:29,030 --> 00:03:32,450
I'll make one for you and you
and all of you.

80
00:03:32,490 --> 00:03:34,910
Ooh! And, of course,
Pinkie and Fluttershy, too.

81
00:03:34,950 --> 00:03:36,330
Oh, and when I'm done,

82
00:03:36,330 --> 00:03:38,370
