our very own fashion show!

83
00:03:38,410 --> 00:03:39,490
What a great idea --

84
00:03:39,540 --> 00:03:41,580
If you're sure
you can handle it.

85
00:03:41,620 --> 00:03:43,870
Oh, it'll be
a little bit of work,

86
00:03:43,870 --> 00:03:47,540
but it'll be a wonderful boost
for my business...plus fun!

87
00:03:47,540 --> 00:03:49,590
Oh, I love fun things!

88
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:51,010
Then it's settled.

89
00:03:51,050 --> 00:03:54,340
We'll have a fashion show
starring us!

90
00:03:54,340 --> 00:03:56,600
Yay!
Yay!Yay!
Yay!

91
