For lock and crest *

125
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,600
* Don't forget some magic
In the dress *

126
00:05:28,650 --> 00:05:30,650
* Even though it rides high
On the flank *

127
00:05:30,690 --> 00:05:32,730
* Rainbow won't look
Like a tank *

128
