* Wait until you see it
In the light *

233
00:09:43,530 --> 00:09:47,360
* I'm sewing them together

234
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:49,450
Don't you think my gown
would be more me

235
00:09:49,490 --> 00:09:50,530
with some lollipops?

236
00:09:50,570 --> 00:09:52,280
Well, I think --
Balloons?

237
00:09:52,330 --> 00:09:53,990
Well...
Do it!

238
