* I'm sewing them together

241
00:10:00,130 --> 00:10:02,090
* Take great pains

242
00:10:02,130 --> 00:10:04,300
* Fluttershy,
You're putting me in a bind *

243
00:10:04,300 --> 00:10:06,340
* Rainbow Dash,
What is on your mind? *

244
00:10:06,380 --> 00:10:08,840
* Oh, my gosh,
There's simply not much time *

245
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:14,310
* Don't forget,
Applejack's duds must shine *

246
00:10:14,350 --> 00:10:16,180
* Dressmaking's easy

247
00:10:16,220 --> 00:10:18,190
