248
00:10:18,230 --> 00:10:20,190
* Brings a whole new revision

249
00:10:20,230 --> 00:10:23,110
* Have to pick up the pace,
Still hold to my vision *

250
00:10:23,150 --> 00:10:27,360
That constellation
is canis major, not minor.

251
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:30,570
French haute couture,
please.

252
00:10:30,610 --> 00:10:32,530
Eh...

253
00:10:33,990 --> 00:10:35,450
What if it rains?

254
00:10:35,490 --> 00:10:37,410
Galoshes!

255
00:10:37,450 --> 00:10:38,500
More balloons!

256
00:10:38,540 --> 00:10:40,000
Oh, no.
That's too many balloons.

257
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:42,130
More candy!
Oh, less candy!

258
00:10:42,170 --> 00:10:44,090
Oh, wait, I know --
Streamers!

259
00:10:44,130 --> 00:10:45,460
Streamers?

260
00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:47,340
Whose dress is this?

